text:
Season 0, Episode 1

Gabrielle Union and Dwyane Wade are getting into the flipping game for a good cause. They find a promising single-story home in the up-and-coming neighborhood of Biscayne Park that could fetch big bucks, but this flip isn't going to be easy. The house is way too small, the backyard is overgrown and the costs are quickly adding up. With a little luck and a lot of hard work, however, this home will be a slam dunk!
title: All Star Flip

meta_data.description: Actress Gabrielle Union and Miami Heat basketball player Dwyane Wade are taking their passion for style to new heights -- flipping homes. Follow along as the couple goes from red carpet to renovation to take on their first project in a suburban Florida neighborhood. And when these icons have a difference of opinion, the ball is in anyone's court.
